We review the supply, coupon, and redemption picture for the US, UK, Euro, JPY, AUS, NZ, and CAN government bond markets over the next month. This week, G7 net DV01 is expected to be \(\) 47.8m\(/bp, compared to an average*\) \ \(67.9m / bp\) ; US \(\) 4.5m\(/bp; Euro\) \ \(16.1m / bp\) ; Japan \(\) 21.9m / bp; UK \(\) 11.8m / bp\$

In the euro area, we estimate about €26bn of issuance against €7.5bn coupons and no redemptions coming into the market during this week. We expect €114.5bn of supply in the coming five weeks against €14.8bn in coupons and €37.6bn in redemptions, resulting in net issuance of €62.1bn.

In the UK, we expect issuance of UKT via syndication for an estimated £10bn during this week. Additionally, UKTI 0.625% March 2045 will be issued for an estimated £0.8bn. This will be against no cash flow coming into the market.

In the US, there will be not be any issuance during the coming week. There will be a cash flow of \(\) 17.9bn\(in coupons and\) \ \(134.8bn\) in redemptions coming into the market. Over the next five weeks, we expect \(\) 334bn\(of supply against\) \ \(40.2bn\) in coupons and \(\) 315bn\(in redemptions, resulting in net negative issuance of\) \ \(21.3bn\)

In Japan, there will be an issuance of 10y JGB for an estimated \(\) 2.6\(trn and 30y JGB for an estimated\) \ \(0.7trn\) during the coming week. These will be against \(\) 8.8bn\(coupons and\) \ \(2.9trn\) redemptions coming into the market.

In Australia, ACGB 4.25% Jun 2034 will be issued for \(\) 0.3bn\(, ACGB 4.25% Mar 2036 will be issued for\) \ \(1bn\) and ACGB 1.5% Jun 2031 will be issued for \(\) 0.9bn\(during the coming week. These will be against no coupons and no redemptions coming into the market.
In New Zealand, we expect NZGB to be issued for an estimated \(\) 0.45bn\(during the coming week. There will be no cash flow coming into the market.
In Canada, \(5y\) CAN will be issued for an \(\) 5.25bn\(during the coming week. There will be a cash flow of\) \ \(2.6bn\) in coupons and \(\) 47.5bn\(in redemptions.
Note: \*Average Net DV01 (gross issuance less coupons less redemptions plus purchases less sales) issuance over the coming five weeks and past four weeks.
